<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head lang="en">
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="description" content="hello">
    <meta name="keywords" content="a,b,c">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="email=no" />
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no" />
    <title>景区介绍</title>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="content/js/cord.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="content/css/common.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="content/css/font-awesome.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="content/css/audio.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="content/css/jqjs.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="content/css/jdjs.css" />
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
    <script src="http://apps.bdimg.com/libs/html5shiv/3.7/html5shiv.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
</head>

<body>
	<div class="content">
		<div class="img-box">
			<p>青城山</p>
			<img src="content/images/img02.jpg" alt="" />
		</div>

		<article class="info">
			<figure>
				<figcaption>青城山景点介绍</figcaption>
			</figure>

			<p class="intro">
				青城山位于四川省成都平原西北部，东距成都68公里，距
				都江堰仅10多公里。主峰老霄顶海拔1600米。青城山因其
				四季常青，满目青翠，诸峰环峙，状若城廓而得名，素有"
				青城天下幽"之美誉，与剑门之险、峨嵋之秀、夔门之雄齐
				名。青城山分青城前山和青城后山。前山景色优美，文物
				古迹众多；后山自然景物神秘绮丽、原始华美如世外桃源
				青城山靠岷山雪岭，面向川西平原后山。前山景色优美，
				古迹众多；后山自然景物神秘绮丽、原始华美如世外桃源
				青城山靠岷山雪岭，面向川西平原。
			</p>
		</article>

		<div class="audio-box">
			<h4>讲解试听</h4>

			<div class="audio-listed">
				<ol>
					<li data-src="content/audio/fukua.mp3" data-title="fukua" data-cover="content/images/img02.jpg">
						<img src="content/images/audio_icon.png" alt="" />
						天师洞
					</li>
					<li data-src="http://jq22com.qiniudn.com/jq22m1.mp3" data-title="china" data-cover="content/images/img02.jpg">
						<img src="content/images/audio_icon.png" alt="" />
						天师洞
					</li>
					<li data-src="http://jq22.qiniudn.com/2_01.mp3" data-title="笑脸" data-cover="content/images/img02.jpg">
						<img src="content/images/audio_icon.png" alt="" />
						天师洞
					</li>
					<li data-src="content/audio/fukua.mp3" data-title="fukua" data-cover="content/images/img02.jpg">
						<img src="content/images/audio_icon.png" alt="" />
						天师洞
					</li>
					<div class="clear"></div>
				</ol>
			</div>
		</div>	
	</div>

	<div class="audio-fixed-box">
		<div class="audio-container">
			<div class="audio-view">
				<div class="audio-cover"></div>
				<div class="audio-body">
					<h3 class="audio-title">未知歌曲</h3>
					<div class="audio-backs">
						<div class="audio-this-time">00:00</div>
						<div class="audio-count-time">00:00</div>
						<div class="audio-setbacks">
							<i class="audio-this-setbacks">
								<span class="audio-backs-btn"></span>
							</i>
							<span class="audio-cache-setbacks">
							</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="audio-btn" style="display: none;">
					<div class="audio-select">
						<div action="prev" class="icon-fast-backward"></div>
						<div action="play" data-on="icon-play" data-off="icon-pause" class="icon-play"></div>
						<div action="next" class="icon-fast-forward"></div>
						<!--<div action="menu" class="icon-list-alt"></div>-->
						<div action="volume" class="icon-volume-up">
							<div class="audio-set-volume">
								<div class="volume-box">
									<i><span  class="audio-backs-btn"></span></i>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<a class="audio-close" href="javascript: ">关闭</a>
	</div>

	<script type="text/javascript" src="content/js/jquery-1.11.1.min.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="content/js/audio.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="content/js/public.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript">
		window.onload = function() {
			var audioFn;

			$('.audio-listed li').on('click', function () {
				var src = $(this).attr('data-src');
				var cover = $(this).attr('data-cover');
				var title = $(this).attr('data-title');

				var setConfig = {
					song : [
						{
							title : title,
							src : src, // 文件路径
							cover : cover // 封面图片;
						}
					],
					error : function(meg){
						console.log(meg);
					}
				};

				audioFn = audioPlay(setConfig); // 预加载
				audioFn.loadFile(true);
				$('.audio-fixed-box').fadeIn(50);
			})

			$('.audio-close').on('click', function () {
				audioFn.play(false);
				$('.audio-fixed-box').fadeOut(50);
			})
		}
	</script>
</body>
</html>